title: University Library Level 3: Libraries - Northwestern University
content: Text version Reserve Classroom 3622. Northwestern University faculty, administration and Library staff can reserve the Ver Steeg Faculty Lounge for special receptions and other formal social events. Capacity for 41 people seated or standing room for 70 people. See more about Ver Steeg, or submit a request with the Libraries event space request form. Reserve Classroom 3322.
